cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software or the paper's ideas, please cite it."
title: "Composable Trust for Language Models"
abstract: >-
  A proven authority boundary plus a measured, prompt-tuned defense against prompt
  injection for language models: a single frozen model wrapped in a deterministic
  pipeline that enforces a Biba integrity lattice, with authority non-interference
  proved by exhaustion over the finite lattice.
authors:
